{
  "stem": "15694.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was going on during the sort of, you know, whatever-- so, you know, telling that up to the point we went into Bochnia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Bochnia, a small town, for some reason we had more to eat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, we had one room about-- it's in my book, I think. 4 by-- 3 and 1/2 by 6 meters, roughly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was in the small room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lived there, and we had to wash there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had corners.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had a corner where there was a stove which was for warmth and for cooking.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one day, we had an arrival.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "However he came across to us, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My grandfather arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My grandfather from Germany, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was also in the tunnel, and he managed to stay-- to go back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyway, he arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "How, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But soon, our joy turned into something less than that because he was 10 years a-- a widower, and he found a woman.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he married her by the-- by the age of 67.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she moved in with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "A double wardrobe the size-- the width of a bed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We turned sideways, behind which they had their bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We moved into another corner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I slept in a mattress on the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My-- my sister, little sister, slept with the parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So now we were six in that room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now, this good lady, we would have-- a very nice lady, would have congratulated him to his good taste and good fortune after being 10 years a widower.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But this good lady had a-- a brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And my grandfather brought along some money as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But it soon run out.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
